<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Cour-supreme-du-Canada_PLD_20110511_088.8001.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3412" alt="Cour supreme" src="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Cour-supreme-du-Canada_PLD_20110511_088.8001.jpg" width="480" height="319" /></a></p>
